    "This is illustrated in Figure 4b showing the distribution of the norm of the difference of forces between FeNNix-Bio1(M) and the distilled model along an STS trajectory of the protein-ligand system.",
    "We observe a dense distribution of values close to 0 kcal/mol/ Å and a long-tailed distribution starting from 150 kcal/mol/ Å.",
    "The latter is associated with large nonphysical force discrepancies yielding the infrequent instabilities that we observe in the DMTS simulation.",
    "To address this limitation, we introduce two complementary strategies:",
